visitTypes.name: Adult HIV Initial Visit
visitTypes.message: Patient has to be 20yrs and above, in the location he enrolled into the HIV Care and Treatment program and there must not be prior clinical encounter.

visitTypes.name: Adult Transfer In Visit
visitTypes.message: Patient has to be 20yrs and above , patient's program location should be equal to the last HIV clinical encounter location and should not be the first clinical encounter

visitTypes.name: Adult HIV Return Visit
visitTypes.message: Patient has to be 20yrs and above, in the location he enrolled into the HIV Care and Treatment program  and there must be a prior clinical encounter.

visitTypes.name: Pediatric HIV Initial Visit
visitTypes.message: Patient has to be 14rs and below ,in the location he enrolled into the HIV Care and Treatment program and there must not be prior clinical encounter.

visitTypes.name: Pediatric HIV Return Visit
visitTypes.message: Patient has to be 14yrs and below, in the location enrolled into the HIV Care and Treatment program and it must not be the initial clinical encounter.
